version_description: I have never seen Chords for this SOng so i made them myself. Hope you like it:).
Version is also for beginners to play but close to the original.
Easier to play a different key.
There are a few differences in the chords, for example the first chord transition in the chorus is from E to D, not E to G. I'm happy to make corrections if you don't mind explaining why.
Only chord version on ultimate guitar, good for keyboards or an acoustic version.
